[05/07/2019 11:31:31] <font color="#ffffff">(CANTAN)</font>
[05/07/2019 11:31:47] <font color="#ffffff">Aquí ponemos ropa de chica,</font>
[05/07/2019 11:31:50] <font color="#ffffff">aquí de chico</font>
