[05/07/2019 19:33:21] <font color="#ffffff">No pasa nada.</font>
[05/07/2019 19:33:21] <font color="#ffff00">Perfecto.</font>
[05/07/2019 19:33:25] <font color="#ffff00">Va a añadir el arroz.</font>
